        <dc:title>Load representation for dynamic performance analysis (of power systems)</dc:title>
        <dcterms:abstract>The current state of the art of power system load representation for dynamic performance analysis is reviewed. Terminology is defined, the importance of load modeling is discussed, and important considerations for different types of loads and different types of analyses are examined.&lt;&gt;</dcterms:abstract>
