        <dc:title>Residential load characteristics observed at KEPCO power system</dc:title>
        <dcterms:abstract>Residential load characteristics are studied, and those load characteristics that are important for power system studies are identified. The results are used to determine the load model parameters and their statistical correlation to the load composition is presented separately.&lt;&gt;</dcterms:abstract>
